[http://www.dd-wrt.com/phpBB2/viewtopic.php?t=170071 On the DD-WRT forums] (w/ internal pictures) :16MB Winbond W9812G2GH-6 + 8MB EtronTech EM638325TS-6 > 24MB total RAM :Z-Com XG-623G wireless module (the FCC ID and FCC date of the XG-623G has been applied to this entry) :"TurBoard" appears to be silkscreened on the main board. Default settings are per '''Micronet''''s manual. :The sample SSID specified in the manual is '''wireless'''. The OUIs used are 00:05:B4 ('''Aceex''') for WAN/LAN and 02:05:B4 for WLAN. Both OUIs have a fair number of '''wireless''' SSIDs attributed to them in the '''WiGLE''' DB.
